"while running.  Avoid high-demand periods when scheduling `scrub` or use "
"<<zfs-advanced-tuning-scrub_delay,`vfs.zfs.scrub_delay`>> to adjust the "
"relative priority of the `scrub` to keep it from slowing down other "
"workloads."
msgstr ""
