#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/zfs/_index.adoc:1459
msgid ""
"The `zfs` utility can create, destroy, and manage all existing ZFS datasets "
"within a pool.  To manage the pool itself, use <<zfs-zpool,`zpool`>>."
