#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/zfs/_index.adoc:1791
msgid ""
"Snapshots are not shown by a normal `zfs list` operation.  To list "
"snapshots, append `-t snapshot` to `zfs list`.  `-t all` displays both file "
